      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking for a new home for my trusty car! It\u2019s been such a reliable partner for me and is still in really solid shape. It\u2019s got that 'well-loved' feel but drives beautifully and has plenty of life left for all your road trips. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I\u2019m excited for someone else to enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I\u2019d love to tell you more about it!",
