    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 inline-six powerplant. This unit has been meticulously maintained with a focus on mechanical longevity; the Vanos system has been overhauled, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to ensure chassis rigidity. Power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock. Suspension geometry remains true with recent bushing replacements and upgraded dampers. While the aesthetic reflects its status as a driven machine, the drivetrain remains robust, offering linear power delivery and a visceral 8,000 RPM redline. A perfect candidate for a purist seeking a mechanically sound, high-performance platform.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
