    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 2015 BMW M3 in iconic Yas Marina Blue is the perfect blend of track-ready performance and daily sophistication. The exterior paint retains a brilliant, deep shine, though close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel\u2014typical for a car that has been enjoyed but respected. Inside, the Silverstone extended leather interior remains supple and clean, with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s seat bolster and pristine carbon fiber trim throughout. Mechanically, this M3 is in excellent health; the S55 twin-turbo engine pulls hard across the rev range, and the dual-clutch transmission delivers lightning-fast shifts. It has been strictly serviced at 5,000-mile intervals, with a recently completed brake service and a fresh set of Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires. All electronics, including the Harman Kardon sound system and Head-Up Display, function perfectly. This is a well-sorted, honest example of a modern legend, ready for its next owner to turn the key and drive.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
